BingDocumentSourceDescriptor
public static class BingDocumentSourceDescriptor.AttributeBuilder
extends MultipageSearchEngineDescriptor.AttributeBuilder

Attribute map builder for the BingDocumentSource component. You can use this builder as a type-safe alternative to populating the attribute map using attribute keys.

options

public BingDocumentSourceDescriptor.AttributeBuilder options(String value)
Miscellaneous request options. Bing provides the following options:
  • DisableLocationDetection
  • EnableHighlighting

Options should be space-separated.
